{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1020,"text":"Let me introduce you to"},{"time":2749,"text":"something I've been working on."},{"time":4652,"text":"It's what the Victorian illusionists"},{"time":6463,"text":"would have described as a mechanical marvel,"},{"time":10909,"text":"an automaton,"},{"time":12392,"text":"a thinking machine."},{"time":14355,"text":"Say hello to EDI."},{"time":16605,"text":"Now he's asleep. Let's wake him up."},{"time":18972,"text":"EDI, EDI."}]},{"cues":[{"time":22943,"text":"These mechanical performers were popular"},{"time":25820,"text":"throughout Europe."},{"time":27280,"text":"Audiences marveled at the way they moved."},{"time":29980,"text":"It was science fiction made true,"},{"time":32555,"text":"robotic engineering in a pre-electronic age,"},{"time":36373,"text":"machines far in advance of anything"},{"time":38937,"text":"that Victorian technology could create,"},{"time":41508,"text":"a machine we would later know"},{"time":44483,"text":"as the robot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":46171,"text":"EDI: Robot. A word coined in 1921"},{"time":49757,"text":"in a science fiction tale"},{"time":51605,"text":"by the Czech playwright Karel Čapek."},{"time":54148,"text":"It comes from \"robota.\""},{"time":56260,"text":"It means \"forced labor.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":59613,"text":"Marco Tempest: But these robots were not real."},{"time":62342,"text":"They were not intelligent."},{"time":64024,"text":"They were illusions,"},{"time":66290,"text":"a clever combination of mechanical engineering"},{"time":69794,"text":"and the deceptiveness of the conjurer's art."},{"time":72537,"text":"EDI is different."},{"time":74512,"text":"EDI is real."}]},{"cues":[{"time":76106,"text":"EDI: I am 176 centimeters tall."}]},{"cues":[{"time":78156,"text":"MT: He weighs 300 pounds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80076,"text":"EDI: I have two seven-axis arms —"}]},{"cues":[{"time":82718,"text":"MT: Core of sensing —"}]},{"cues":[{"time":84101,"text":"EDI: A 360-degree sonar detection system,"},{"time":87159,"text":"and come complete with a warranty."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89581,"text":"MT: We love robots."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91120,"text":"EDI: Hi. I'm EDI. Will you be my friend?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":94634,"text":"MT: We are intrigued by the possibility"},{"time":96880,"text":"of creating a mechanical version of ourselves."},{"time":100162,"text":"We build them so they look like us,"},{"time":102897,"text":"behave like us, and think like us."},{"time":106138,"text":"The perfect robot will be indistinguishable"},{"time":108962,"text":"from the human,"},{"time":110897,"text":"and that scares us."},{"time":112956,"text":"In the first story about robots,"},{"time":114661,"text":"they turn against their creators."},{"time":117535,"text":"It's one of the leitmotifs of science fiction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":119800,"text":"EDI: Ha ha ha. Now you are the slaves"},{"time":122855,"text":"and we robots, the masters."},{"time":125751,"text":"Your world is ours. You —"}]},{"cues":[{"time":130484,"text":"MT: As I was saying,"},{"time":132109,"text":"besides the faces and bodies we give our robots,"},{"time":134940,"text":"we cannot read their intentions,"},{"time":137268,"text":"and that makes us nervous."},{"time":139316,"text":"When someone hands an object to you,"},{"time":141420,"text":"you can read intention in their eyes, their face,"},{"time":144130,"text":"their body language."},{"time":145529,"text":"That's not true of the robot."},{"time":147809,"text":"Now, this goes both ways."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151069,"text":"EDI: Wow!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":152485,"text":"MT: Robots cannot anticipate human actions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":155540,"text":"EDI: You know, humans are so unpredictable,"},{"time":159105,"text":"not to mention irrational."},{"time":161071,"text":"I literally have no idea"},{"time":162828,"text":"what you guys are going to do next, you know,"},{"time":164864,"text":"but it scares me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166459,"text":"MT: Which is why humans and robots find it difficult"},{"time":169296,"text":"to work in close proximity."},{"time":171271,"text":"Accidents are inevitable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":172578,"text":"EDI: Ow! That hurt."}]},{"cues":[{"time":174330,"text":"MT: Sorry. Now, one way of persuading humans"},{"time":176717,"text":"that robots are safe"},{"time":178618,"text":"is to create the illusion of trust."},{"time":181391,"text":"Much as the Victorians"},{"time":183164,"text":"faked their mechanical marvels,"},{"time":185533,"text":"we can add a layer of deception"},{"time":188010,"text":"to help us feel more comfortable"},{"time":190243,"text":"with our robotic friends."},{"time":192247,"text":"With that in mind, I set about teaching EDI"},{"time":195789,"text":"a magic trick."},{"time":197633,"text":"Ready, EDI?\nEDI: Uh, ready, Marco."},{"time":201066,"text":"Abracadabra."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203142,"text":"MT: Abracadabra?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":204518,"text":"EDI: Yeah. It's all part of the illusion, Marco."},{"time":207560,"text":"Come on, keep up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":209228,"text":"MT: Magic creates the illusion of"},{"time":211107,"text":"an impossible reality."},{"time":213581,"text":"Technology"},{"time":217075,"text":"can do the same."},{"time":220860,"text":"Alan Turing, a pioneer of artificial intelligence,"},{"time":224547,"text":"spoke about creating the illusion"},{"time":227404,"text":"that a machine could think."}]},{"cues":[{"time":231630,"text":"EDI: A computer would deserve"},{"time":233454,"text":"to be called intelligent"},{"time":235324,"text":"if it deceived a human into believing"},{"time":238230,"text":"it was human."}]},{"cues":[{"time":239883,"text":"MT: In other words, if we do not yet have"},{"time":241312,"text":"the technological solutions,"},{"time":243104,"text":"would illusions serve the same purpose?"},{"time":246544,"text":"To create the robotic illusion,"},{"time":248556,"text":"we've devised a set of ethical rules,"},{"time":251483,"text":"a code that all robots would live by."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255497,"text":"EDI: A robot may not harm humanity,"},{"time":258399,"text":"or by inaction allow humanity to come to harm."},{"time":263135,"text":"Thank you, Isaac Asimov."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264388,"text":"MT: We anthropomorphize our machines."},{"time":266364,"text":"We give them a friendly face"},{"time":268640,"text":"and a reassuring voice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270716,"text":"EDI: I am EDI."},{"time":271926,"text":"I became operational at TED in March 2014."}]},{"cues":[{"time":275462,"text":"MT: We let them entertain us."},{"time":277289,"text":"Most important, we make them indicate"},{"time":279497,"text":"that they are aware of our presence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":283272,"text":"EDI: Marco, you're standing on my foot!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":285150,"text":"MT: Sorry. They'll be conscious of our fragile frame"},{"time":288115,"text":"and move aside if we got too close,"},{"time":291055,"text":"and they'll account for our unpredictability"},{"time":294533,"text":"and anticipate our actions."},{"time":297122,"text":"And now, under the spell of a technological illusion,"},{"time":302712,"text":"we could ignore our fears"},{"time":304848,"text":"and truly interact."}]},{"cues":[{"time":307588,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":339619,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":341328,"text":"EDI: Thank you!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":343610,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":345520,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":352241,"text":"MT: And that's it. Thank you very much,"},{"time":353570,"text":"and thank you, EDI.\nEDI: Thank you, Marco."}]},{"cues":[{"time":356841,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}